graph LR
    MROperator[Model Registry Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    MROperator -->|SQL backend<br/>5432/TCP| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 9.6+]
    MROperator -->|SQL backend<br/>3306/TCP| MySQL[MySQL 5.7+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - OpenShift)
    MROperator -.->|TLS certs<br/>auto-provision| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA 4.x]
    MROperator -.->|OAuth auth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS| OSAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server 4.x]
    MROperator -.->|external routes<br/>443/TCP| OSRouter[OpenShift Ingress Router 4.x]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    MROperator -->|deploys instances| ModelRegistrySvc[odh-model-registry service]
    MROperator -.->|metrics scraping<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Platform[opendatahub-operator /<br/>rhods-operator] -->|watches platform CRD<br/>components.platform.opendatahub.io| MROperator

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management<br/>optional| ModelRegistrySvc
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|model metadata<br/>integration| ModelRegistrySvc

    %% Kubernetes Core
    MROperator -->|CR reconciliation<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    MROperator -.->|webhook certs<br/>optional| CertManager[cert-manager 1.13+]

    %% External Clients
    DataScientist[Data Scientists /<br/>ML Engineers] -->|creates CRs<br/>kubectl/oc| MROperator
    DataScientist -->|REST API calls<br/>8080/8443| ModelRegistrySvc

    %% Styling
    style MROperator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style PostgreSQL fill:#336791,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style MySQL fill:#00758f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style ServiceCA fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OSAuth fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OSRouter fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style ModelRegistrySvc fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#e6522c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Platform fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style CertManager fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
